## Agent 事件流详细

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户
    participant Sessions as Sessions.vue
    participant SSE as useSessionEvents
    participant Router as session.py Router
    participant GenSvc as generate_service
    participant AgentSvc as agent_service
    participant Bridge as agent_bridge
    participant TaskMgr as task_manager
    participant EventLog as EventLog
    participant LLM as LLM API
    participant Tool as Tools (4个)
    participant BillingSvc as billing_service

    User->>Sessions: 点击生成(Agent模式)
    Sessions->>Router: POST /api/sessions/{id}/generate<br/>{agent_mode:true, prompt, ...}
    Router->>GenSvc: handle_agent_generate(data)
    GenSvc->>GenSvc: parse_agent_intent(prompt)<br/>8级正则解析意图
    GenSvc->>GenSvc: resolve_context_references()<br/>解析参考图URL

    alt single策略
        GenSvc->>GenSvc: _execute_single()
    else parallel策略
        GenSvc->>GenSvc: execute_multi_independent()
    else iterative策略
        GenSvc->>GenSvc: _generate_iterative_steps()
        GenSvc->>GenSvc: execute_iterative()
    else radiate策略
        GenSvc->>GenSvc: _generate_radiate_params()
        GenSvc->>GenSvc: _execute_radiate()
    end

    GenSvc->>AgentSvc: run_agent_loop()<br/>(max_rounds=5)
    AgentSvc->>TaskMgr: publish(task_started)

    loop 每轮循环 (max 5轮)
        AgentSvc->>AgentSvc: 令牌预算截断(6000)
        AgentSvc->>LLM: chat_stream_with_tools()<br/>round 0-1: tool_choice=required<br/>round 2+: tool_choice=auto

        loop 流式Token
            LLM-->>AgentSvc: token chunk
            AgentSvc->>Bridge: TokenEvent
            Bridge->>TaskMgr: publish(LamEvent)<br/>event_type=task_progress<br/>payload.type=agent_token
            TaskMgr->>EventLog: append(event)
            TaskMgr-->>SSE: asyncio.Queue推送
            SSE-->>Sessions: SSE data
        end

        alt LLM返回tool_calls
            AgentSvc->>Bridge: ToolCallEvent
            Bridge->>TaskMgr: publish<br/>payload.type=agent_tool_call

            alt tool.checkpoint == true
                AgentSvc->>TaskMgr: set_checkpoint_event()
                AgentSvc->>Bridge: CheckpointEvent
                Bridge->>TaskMgr: publish<br/>event_type=checkpoint_required<br/>payload.type=agent_checkpoint
                TaskMgr-->>SSE: 推送
                SSE-->>Sessions: 显示CheckpointOverlay
                Sessions->>Router: POST /agent/checkpoint<br/>{action:"approve"}
                Router->>TaskMgr: resolve_checkpoint(approved=true)
                TaskMgr-->>AgentSvc: wait_checkpoint()返回true
            end

            AgentSvc->>Tool: execute(**kwargs)
            Tool-->>AgentSvc: ToolResult
            AgentSvc->>Bridge: ToolResultEvent
            Bridge->>TaskMgr: publish<br/>payload.type=agent_tool_result
            AgentSvc->>BillingSvc: record_billing(tool调用)
        else LLM无tool_calls
            AgentSvc->>AgentSvc: 循环结束
        end
    end

    AgentSvc->>Bridge: DoneEvent<br/>{tokens_in, tokens_out, cost}
    Bridge->>TaskMgr: publish(LamEvent)<br/>event_type=task_completed<br/>payload.type=agent_done
    TaskMgr->>EventLog: append(event)
    TaskMgr-->>SSE: 推送
    SSE-->>Sessions: 更新AgentStreamCard状态
    AgentSvc-->>GenSvc: 返回结果
    GenSvc->>GenSvc: validate_agent_result()
    GenSvc->>GenSvc: add_system_message(agent类型)
    GenSvc-->>Router: 返回生成结果
    Router-->>Sessions: HTTP 200
```

