## 意图解析优先级

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start[parse_agent_intent<br/>输入: prompt, image_count<br/>context_messages, reference_labels] --> P1

    P1{Priority 1: radiate<br/>套图/一组/系列<br/>统一风格/同角色/表情包}
    P1 -->|匹配| R1[task_type=radiate<br/>strategy=radiate]

    P1 -->|不匹配| P2{Priority 2: iterative<br/>先...再...最后<br/>草图精修/基于上一张}
    P2 -->|匹配| R2[task_type=iterative<br/>strategy=iterative]

    P2 -->|不匹配| P3{Priority 3: multi_independent<br/>三视图+方向枚举<br/>不同风格/分别画<br/>N张+列表}
    P3 -->|匹配| R3[task_type=multi_independent<br/>strategy=parallel<br/>提取items列表]

    P3 -->|不匹配| P4{Priority 4: single<br/>默认/变体/多张同风格}
    P4 -->|匹配| R4[task_type=single<br/>strategy=single]

    R1 --> Route[策略路由]
    R2 --> Route
    R3 --> Route
    R4 --> Route

    Route --> S1{single}
    S1 -->|执行| E1[_execute_single<br/>直接generate_images_core]

    Route --> S2{parallel}
    S2 -->|执行| E2[execute_multi_independent<br/>并行generate_image工具调用]

    Route --> S3{iterative}
    S3 -->|执行| E3[_generate_iterative_steps<br/>LLM生成步骤<br/>+ execute_iterative<br/>顺序执行+参考图传递]

    Route --> S4{radiate}
    S4 -->|执行| E4[_generate_radiate_params<br/>LLM生成辐射参数<br/>+ _execute_radiate<br/>锚点网格→裁切→扩展]

    classDef priority fill:#FFCDD2,stroke:#C62828,stroke-width:2px
    classDef result fill:#C8E6C9,stroke:#2E7D32,stroke-width:2px
    classDef strategy fill:#E1BEE7,stroke:#6A1B9A,stroke-width:2px

    class P1,P2,P3,P4 priority
    class R1,R2,R3,R4 result
    class E1,E2,E3,E4 strategy
```

